<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE document PUBLIC "-//APACHE//DTD Documentation V1.1//EN" "document-v11.dtd">
<document>
  <header>
    <title>Royal Mail Customer Barcode</title>
  </header>
  <body>
    <section id="example">
      <title>Example</title>
      <figure src="../images/example-royal-mail-cbc.png" alt="Example Royal Mail Customer Barcode symbol"/>
    </section>
    <section id="structure">
      <title>Structure</title>
      <p>The configuration for the default implementation is:</p>
      <source>&#60;barcode&#62;
  &#60;<strong>royal-mail-cbc</strong>&#62;
      &#60;module-width&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:0.53mm}&#60;/module-width&#62;
      &#60;track-height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:1.25mm}&#60;/track-height&#62;
      &#60;ascender-height&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:1.25mm}&#60;/ascender-height&#62;
      &#60;interchar-gap-width&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:1mw}&#60;/interchar-gap-width&#62;
      &#60;quiet-zone enabled="{<link href="barcode-xml.html#boolean">boolean</link>:true}"&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#length">length</link>:10mw}&#60;/quiet-zone&#62;
      &#60;checksum&#62;{<link href="barcode-xml.html#checksum-mode">checksum-mode</link>:auto=add}&#60;/checksum&#62;
  &#60;/<strong>royal-mail-cbc</strong>&#62;
&#60;/barcode&#62;</source>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Notes</title>
      <ul>
        <li>This symbology has no human-readable part!</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Message format</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Valid characters are 0-9 and A-Z</li>
        <li>Start and stop characters are: ( [ ] ) (they are added automatically as necessary)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Links</title>
      <ul>
        <li>Specification: <link href="http://www.mailsorttechnical.com/">http://www.mailsorttechnical.com/</link> (Look for "Mailsort 700" under "Downloads" and "Mailsort user guide")</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </body>
</document>

